<topic id="results-view">
  <title>Results View</title>
  <prolog>
    <metadata>
      <keywords>
        <indexterm>Results view</indexterm>
      </keywords>
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
  <body>
    <p>The <uicontrol>Results</uicontrol> view displays the messages generated as a result of user
      actions such as validations, transformations, search operations, and others. Each message is a
      link to the location related to the event that triggered the message. Double-clicking a
      message opens the file containing the location and positions the cursor at the location
      offset. The <uicontrol>Results</uicontrol> view is automatically opened when certain actions
      generate result messages.<note type="tip" product="author developer editor">To shift focus to
        the opened <uicontrol>Results</uicontrol> view without using the mouse, there is an action
        in the <menucascade>
          <uicontrol>Window</uicontrol>
          <uicontrol>Results</uicontrol>
        </menucascade> menu called <uicontrol>Focus Results</uicontrol> that can be used for this
        purpose and you can <xref
          href="preferences-menu-shortcut-keys.dita#preferences-menu-shortcut-keys">assign a
          keyboard shortcut</xref> to this action.</note></p>
    <p>The actions that contribute messages to this view include:<ul>
        <li><xref
            href="validation-actions-in-user-interface.dita#validation-actions-in-user-interface"
            format="dita"><uicontrol>Validation</uicontrol> actions</xref></li>
        <li><xref href="transforming-documents.dita#transforming-documents" format="dita"
              ><uicontrol>Transformation</uicontrol> actions</xref></li>
        <li><xref href="spell-check-in-files.dita#spell-check-in-files" format="dita"
              ><uicontrol>Check Spelling in Files</uicontrol> action</xref></li>
        <li><ph product="editor author developer"><uicontrol>Find All</uicontrol> action from the
              <xref href="find-replace-dialog.dita#find-replace-dialog" format="dita"
                ><uicontrol>Find/Replace</uicontrol> dialog box</xref></ph></li>
        <li><ph product="editor author developer"><xref
              href="find-and-replace-text-in-files.dita#find-and-replace-text-in-files"
              format="dita"><uicontrol>Find/Replace in Files</uicontrol> dialog box</xref></ph></li>
        <li product="editor editorEclipse developer developerEclipse"><xref
            href="find-xslt-references-and-declarations.dita#find-xslt-references-and-declarations"
            format="dita"><uicontrol>Search References</uicontrol> action</xref></li>
        <li product="editor author developer"><xref href="xpath-console.dita#xpath-console"
            format="dita">XPath expression results</xref></li>
        <li><xref href="executing-sql-statements.dita#executing-sql-statements" format="dita">SQL
            results</xref></li>
      </ul></p>
